      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides consistent, predictable shifts. Inside, the cabin is clean with only minor signs of wear on the upholstery, and all major electronics and climate controls are fully functional. The exterior retains a nice shine, though there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. It is a solid choice for anyone seeking a reliable vehicle that is ready for the road.",
