    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s seriously in incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 showcases the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. Power is delivered via the legendary 13B-REW twin-rotor engine, featuring a factory-spec sequential Hitachi twin-turbocharger setup that provides linear torque across the rev range. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by its original four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the vacuum routing for the complex solenoids has been meticulously maintained to ensure seamless turbo transition. The interior preserves the driver-centric cockpit with zero bolster wear, and the exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation. A true turnkey example for the rotary purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen. The exterior features a flawless factory finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent, with premium leather upholstery that shows zero signs of wear, bolster creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. This car has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. Included in the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder documenting every scheduled service performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. For the buyer seeking mechanical and aesthetic perfection, this vehicle offers a like-new experience without the first-year depreciation.",
      "price": 43900.0,
